<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A <rs type="objectType">panel</rs> blackened and worn by weathering (H. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.77</measure>, W. <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.98</measure>, D <measure precision="circa" dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.25</measure>) figuring a gable in flat relief with a <rs type="decoration">tabella ansata</rs> outlined in similar relief below it.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Inscribed on the relief of the gable (l.1) within the gable (ll. 2-3) on the upper moulding of the tabella (ll. 4-5) and within the tabella (ll.6 ff.) The surface is very badly worn.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>II-III. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.015-0.02</measure>. Ligatures: HN, l.2.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p><date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0300" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
